trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of ConfigurationLocationCollection objects.

Use the ConfigurationLocationCollection class to iterate through a collection of <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocation> objects, which represent the resources for which location-specific configuration settings are defined.
trans-unit.target: Bruk ConfigurationLocationCollection-klasse for å gå gjennom en samling av <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocation>objekter, som representerer ressursene som er definert for plassering bestemte konfigurasjonsinnstillinger.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocation>

trans-unit.source: ConfigurationLocationCollection is the type returned by the <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Locations%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: ConfigurationLocationCollection er typen som ble returnert av den <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Locations%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Locations%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The ConfigurationLocationCollection class might not reference the collection of <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocation> objects in the order that they are specified in the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For ConfigurationLocationCollection klassen kan ikke referere til samlingen av <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocation>objekter i rekkefølgen som de er angitt i konfigurasjonsfilen.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocation>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocationCollection"></xref> object at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocationCollection"> </xref> objektet i den angitte indeksen.

trans-unit.source: Use the Item accessor to the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocationCollection> class to get a specific <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocation> object from the collection by specifying its index within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk elementet aksessor til den <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocationCollection>klassen for å få en bestemt <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocation>objektet fra samlingen ved å angi indeksen i samlingen.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocation> </xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocationCollection>

trans-unit.source: The index location of the <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationLocationCollection"></xref> to return.
